{"tid":234451,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"熱刺公佈訪港票價 最平330蚊有得睇","createTime":"2017-05-08T10:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T10:42:19.000Z","uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68cce9049fcbad55742ea6bf3abe2ffcfb6d2f53","tid":234451,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:08:52.000Z","msg":"出爐港超聯盟主傑志今午公佈，英超勁旅熱刺本月26日在香港大球場與傑志進行表演賽，而賽事門票周三公佈發售，票價分680元、480元、330元及180元﹝特惠票﹞。賽事所有收益將全數撥歸傑志慈善基金，作為傑志賽馬會中心發展之用；賽事亦是香港回歸20年的慶祝活動之一。關於賽事售票安排，<a href=\"http://周三10時開始會率先在www.stubhub.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%8910%E6%99%82%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%E6%9C%83%E7%8E%87%E5%85%88%E5%9C%A8www.stubhub.com&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=41e89914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">周三10時開始會率先在www.stubhub.com</a>發售，至本月 <a href=\"http://15日再於www.cityline.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F15%E6%97%A5%E5%86%8D%E6%96%BCwww.cityline.com&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=08f075a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">15日再於www.cityline.com</a>及其他售銷售點發售。<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》則報道，熱刺由領隊普捷天奴至球員等都對漫長賽季結束後馬上又要外訪，且更是長途跋涉遠赴香港感到不滿，但由於熱刺主席利維銳意在東亞地區拓展球隊品牌，故球員亦只能隨隊出訪。熱刺在5月21日將會在聯賽煞科戰作客侯城，這會是球隊季內第53場比賽，熱刺亦將於7月底出訪美國。"},{"pid":"6b86fe3f913bdf7725d6493cf3545213d427c5fb","tid":234451,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:10:46.000Z","msg":"fb 有人話請陳七每邊踢半場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a0c088ca2dbdc3d7c29d695ad192c698d0324b","tid":234451,"uid":22599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:12:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a935d65a8685e32151eba2230c63e79a015c51bf","tid":234451,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:13:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>fb 有人話請陳七每邊踢半場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk